{"type": "article", "id": 15286, "title": "法国人装修一个家，设计师让父亲的归父亲，儿子的归儿子", "description": "两种风格，各有千秋。", "date": "2015-09-22T19:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 16383, "name": "父子房间"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605215952c1UPKxhaWl0drjXZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t法国巴黎有一个单亲家庭，一位年轻的父亲带着年幼的儿子一起生活。他们邀请了设计师 <a href=\"http://www.glennmedioni.com/\">Glenn Medioni</a> ，<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/an-apartment-in-paris-designed-for-a-father-and-his-son/\" target=\"_blank\">将自己的家打造成了风格截然不同的两个空间。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215946MZqU4Wc9niuEsx1B.jpg\" title=\"父与子的房间对比\" alt=\"父与子的房间对比\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>父与子的房间风格对比</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215947mYqzyJeR8isFw50L.jpg\" title=\"儿子的空间\" alt=\"儿子的空间\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>儿子的空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215947N20GfraxmKABCWvO.jpg\" title=\"父亲的小客厅\" alt=\"父亲的小客厅\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>餐厅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052159484nkGOeLlDUPr0C1w.jpg\" title=\"父亲的卧室\" alt=\"父亲的卧室\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>父亲的卧室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215948EYR3Q7kiuXbtZWGs.jpg\" title=\"差距\" alt=\"差距\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>反差</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052159491VZlmTD2GRwKxJ4t.jpg\" title=\"儿子的区域\" alt=\"儿子的区域\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>儿子的区域</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052159499c6D01TK5syIxmF7.jpg\" title=\"双人床铺\" alt=\"双人床铺\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">儿童床铺<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052159503inr0GhYmCyK8dVc.jpg\" title=\"细节\" alt=\"细节\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>细节</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215950e5zWJ2j0vDrfSUP3.jpg\" title=\"玩具\" alt=\"玩具\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>玩具</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215951MRGHAdhn1COEt70D.jpg\" title=\"父亲的洗手间\" alt=\"父亲的洗手间\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>父亲的洗手间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215951pzWZel0QgxqfO6MG.jpg\" title=\"洗手间\" alt=\"洗手间\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>洗手间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>看了这些图后就一个想法：儿子长大了怎么办？再重新装修？十年恍惚一瞬间呐。<span style=\"text-align:left;\">设计师 </span><a href=\"http://www.glennmedioni.com/\">Glenn Medioni</a><span style=\"text-align:left;\"> 还设计过其他作品，比如下图中的这个室内设计：</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215951RZamWBFQt4uPz5Cw.jpg\" title=\"另外一处住宅\" alt=\"另外一处住宅\" data-ratio=\"0.5265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另外一处住宅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/an-apartment-in-paris-designed-for-a-father-and-his-son/\" target=\"_blank\">contemporist</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}